    Digimon. If this effect didn't delete, you may play 1 level 4 or lower [SoC]\_trait
    Digimon card from your trash without paying the cost.\n[All Turns] When one of
    your other [SoC]\_trait Digimon is deleted, this Digimon with an [SoC]\_trait
    Tamer card in its digivolution cards may digivolve into [Fenriloogamon] in the
    trash without paying the cost."
